
---

# `.gitignore`

Use this in your project root:

```gitignore
# Rust
/target
**/*.rs.bk

# Cargo
# Keep Cargo.lock for binaries/app projects
# Remove the next line only if you intentionally want to ignore it
# Cargo.lock

# Environment files
.env
.env.*
!.env.example

# macOS
.DS_Store

# VS Code
.vscode/

# JetBrains
.idea/

# Logs
*.log

# Temporary files
*.tmp
*.temp

# Postgres / local db exports
*.sql
*.dump

# Coverage / profiling
coverage/
*.profraw
*.profdata

# OS generated files
Thumbs.db